{"tid":591211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：矯枉過正？冰室唔肯走飲管即列黑名單 (17:10)","createTime":"2018-03-13T10:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T08:18:26.000Z","uid":17738,"like":128,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"ed09bf8710e982bf5e98a55b3b2ce23eaa950edf","tid":591211,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=IhKlETWeGwy2SRW03p3ARsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a8d2fb29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】人人努力環保，但推廣「走塑」時，一旦意見不合，隨時發生衝突。日前有網民在一間冰室要求「走飲管」失敗，理論期間被店員撥冷水，叫他「唔好咁執着啦！」隨即惹起奉行環保的事主不滿，事後在網上打千字文投訴冰室「走塑不友善」，更要求環保人士將冰室列入黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n網民Leo在Facebook「中伏飲食報料區」發千字文，指在灣仔一間冰室吃早餐時，店員未有按他指示「走飲管」，「豈料數分鐘後，同一店員呈上嚟嘅凍飲卻如常地插住一支塑膠飲管。」令主張環保的Leo大為不滿。<br />\n<br />\n事主即埸表示：「可唔可以將依杯畀咗其他客人先？因為我唔想浪費咗支飲管。」店員在不足5秒後另送上一杯凍飲，事主追問後得知該店員拿來的是同一杯凍飲，只是丟棄了杯中的飲管，以滿足Leo。<br />\n<br />\n由於「未成功走塑」，事主「懷着非常不滿嘅心情，將所有食物打包然後埋單。」該店員見狀，表示「唔好咁執着啦！一支飲管好小事啫&hellip;」事主即再「以更嚴厲嘅語氣向佢哋解釋」，更形容前線飲食業人員有責任負責把關，成為「走塑Friendly（友善）」食肆。<br />\n<br />\nLeo在文末要求冰室採納其建議，並「作出一個令大家都滿意嘅答覆」，否則會成為「走塑不友善黑名單」。<br />\n<br />\n雖有網民讚同他的做法，認為「佢哋真係離晒大譜！做錯事要向客人道歉是常識吧！竟然叫客人唔使為一支飲管咁執着？」但有不少人則直斥事主為「環保塔利班」，矯枉過正。<br />\n<br />\n有人認同走飲管，但不同意將其列入黑名單的手法，「呢個就係點解最近咁多人罵素食者和環保人士嘅原因。」也有人提出「要改變任何嘢都不能一刀切！」東網致電相關冰室，惟冰室職員表示不會接受訪問後隨即掛線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nAnnA Lam：人哋只在乎膠，根本不在乎其他環保因素。<br />\n<br />\nPatrick Luk：素食主義同環保概念，某程度上都係多得你呢啲矯枉過正嘅人令到推行上咁大阻力同被人歧視。<br />\n<br />\nVivian Lam：我估個伙記唔係特登唔同你走，人哋可能慣性動作插咗支飲管落去。環保係好，但真係唔使太執着。有啲嘢係要時間發展。<br />\n<br />\nTaki Chu：其實我都支持走塑，如果真係無走，算。我覺得唔使講咁長嘢同質問人哋。人都有錯，唔記得提返就算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20180313/20180313171016lc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fhknews%2F20180313%2F20180313171016lc.html&d=IhKlETWeGwy2SRW03p3ARsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=814e5e2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20180313/20180313171016lc.html</a>"},{"pid":"56cf329fb7fceec4e205cdc6c9b85509c80e8027","tid":591211,"uid":81500,"like":313,"dislike":3,"score":310,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"打包唔係膠？"},{"pid":"89a4cbc252c3845f55dfffef31b0defe08003ea5","tid":591211,"uid":66260,"like":185,"dislike":0,"score":185,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:29:56.000Z","msg":"環保塔利班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c21dc87e138f0974355af8acf4f4d028e52bdec","tid":591211,"uid":114537,"like":395,"dislike":2,"score":393,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"由於「未成功走塑」，事主「懷着非常不滿嘅心情，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">將所有食物打包</span>然後埋單。」<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bade49fe2e089022a01c481d98acab9238eceb4","tid":591211,"uid":127988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"環保原教旨主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6729f09409ec2e25e90556923b05101107d6f90","tid":591211,"uid":71257,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:33:48.000Z","msg":"打包拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哂多個膠盒 紙杯 膠袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1e7c0dbdc04e3d8e3133499e5f0158477d6cea","tid":591211,"uid":127988,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"3c21dc87e138f0974355af8acf4f4d028e52bdec","tid":591211,"uid":114537,"like":395,"dislike":2,"score":393,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"由於「未成功走塑」，事主「懷着非常不滿嘅心情，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">將所有食物打包</span>然後埋單。」<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"飯盒唔係塑膠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28eb2842bda2dbc5ce907e542835cc75e8faa8cf","tid":591211,"uid":35870,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"56cf329fb7fceec4e205cdc6c9b85509c80e8027","tid":591211,"uid":81500,"like":313,"dislike":3,"score":310,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"打包唔係膠？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能佢自帶盒排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果用即棄膠盒就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d8f39c3c70d85d9941563ad276e629827c1a3a","tid":591211,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"飲水最環保"},{"pid":"6f91fc7665b47aaea7599e006376fa64f5b81c99","tid":591211,"uid":36359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"唔講咩環唔環保先<br />\n但人人心目中都有一份黑名單架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔鐘意咪食囉就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"cc262127a72a8bfcb71b98a29bfc68d9b1b8f288","tid":591211,"uid":531,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"28eb2842bda2dbc5ce907e542835cc75e8faa8cf","tid":591211,"uid":35870,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"56cf329fb7fceec4e205cdc6c9b85509c80e8027","tid":591211,"uid":81500,"like":313,"dislike":3,"score":310,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"打包唔係膠？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h